198→      "symptom": "What went wrong or was confusing — the observable behavior that triggered investigation",
199→      "root_cause": "The underlying technical reason — why it happened",
200→      "takeaway": "The transferable lesson — what to do or avoid in similar situations, useful outside this project",
201→      "applies_when": "Conditions under which this knowledge is relevant (framework version, configuration, etc.)",
202→      "confidence": 80,
203→      "evidence": ["User#7: quoted text...", "Assistant#8: quoted text..."]
204→    }
205→  ]
206→}
207→
208→Only include insights rated 70+ confidence. If you cannot cite evidence, drop the insight. Return empty arrays for categories with no strong insights. Max 3 decisions, 5 learnings.
209→Evidence should reference the labeled turns in the conversation (e.g., "User#2", "Assistant#5").
